(What This Topic Means) Tj
T*
(Git helps developers track code changes and collaborate safely. In Computer Science,) Tj
T*
(students do better when they understand not only the definition of Git, but also the) Tj
T*
(language, symbols, and patterns that appear whenever this topic is tested.) Tj
T*
() Tj
